message: [{"type":"text","text":"<dyad-compaction title=\\"Conversation compacted\\" state=\\"finished\\">\\n## Key Decisions Made\\n- Completed initial task as requested\\n\\n## Current Task State\\nConversation was compacted to save context space.\\n</dyad-compaction>\\n\\nIf you need to retrieve earlier parts of the conversation history, you can read the backup file at: [[compaction-backup-path]]\\nNote: This file may be large. Read only the sections you need or use grep to search for specific content rather than reading the entire file."},{"type":"text","text":"post-compaction step"},{"type":"tool_use","id":"[[TOOL_CALL_0]]","name":"read_file","input":{"path":"SOMEFILE.md"}}]

===
